        in <xref ref="S_direct"></xref>.
        <ul>
          \item If <m>n</m> is an odd integer, then <m>n^2</m> is an odd integer.
        </ul>
      </p>
      <p>
        Now consider the following proposition:
        <ul>
          \item For each integer <m>n</m>, if <m>n^2</m> is an odd integer, then <m>n</m> is an odd integer.
