      </li>
      <li xml:id="exer_sec32-6">
        <p>
          For a right triangle,
          suppose that the hypotenuse has length <m>c</m> feet and the lengths of the sides are <m>a</m> feet and <m>b</m> feet.
          <ol>
            <li>
              <p>
                What is a formula for the area of this right triangle?
                What is an isosceles triangle?
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
